<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Candidate Account - Complete Your Profile</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); padding: 40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #1E293B; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
          
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6 0%, #06B6D4 50%, #F59E0B 100%); padding: 50px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <div style="width: 100px; height: 100px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 100px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
                <span style="font-size: 50px;">üéâ</span>
              </div>
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); letter-spacing: -0.5px;">You've Been Nominated!</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); margin: 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Complete your profile to go live</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 50px 40px;">
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #8B5CF6; padding: 25px; margin: 0 0 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  Hi <span style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8B5CF6, #06B6D4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">{{candidateName}}</span>,
                </p>
                <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  Great news! You've been nominated as a candidate for <strong style="color: #8B5CF6;">{{eventName}}</strong>. A temporary account has been created for you.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Important Warning -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15) 0%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15) 100%); border: 2px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 16px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 35px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px;">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
                <p style="color: #FBBF24; font-size: 16px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700;">IMPORTANT: Temporary Account</p>
                <p style="color: #FDE68A; font-size: 14px; margin: 10px 0 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  You must log in and complete your profile to be visible to voters. Your account will remain inactive until you finish setup.
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 35px;">
                To get started, use these credentials to access your candidate portal:
              </p>

              <!-- Email Credential -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); border: 2px solid #8B5CF6; border-radius: 16px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Email Address</div>
                <div style="background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2); padding: 18px; border-radius: 10px;">
                  <div style="color: #C4B5FD; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; word-break: break-all;">{{email}}</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Password Credential -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); border: 2px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 16px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Temporary Password</div>
                <div style="background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2); padding: 18px; border-radius: 10px;">
                  <div style="color: #FCD34D; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; letter-spacing: 2px;">{{temporaryPassword}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="color: #FDE68A; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 12px;">
                  üîí Change this password immediately after first login
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Next Steps -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 0%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 35px 30px; margin: 35px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 25px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center;">üìã Complete These Steps</h3>
                
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0;">
                      <div style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15); border-left: 4px solid #06B6D4; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
                        <p style="color: #67E8F9; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700;">1Ô∏è‚É£ Click the button below to access your portal</p>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0;">
                      <div style="background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); border-left: 4px solid #10B981; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
                        <p style="color: #6EE7B7; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700;">2Ô∏è‚É£ Log in with your credentials above</p>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0;">
                      <div style="background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15); border-left: 4px solid #8B5CF6; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
                        <p style="color: #C4B5FD; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700;">3Ô∏è‚É£ Change your password to something secure</p>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0;">
                      <div style="background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
                        <p style="color: #FCD34D; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700;">4Ô∏è‚É£ Complete your profile with bio, photos, etc.</p>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0;">
                      <div style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
                        <p style="color: #93C5FD; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; font-weight: 700;">5Ô∏è‚É£ Submit for review and get published!</p>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 35px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6 0%, #06B6D4 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 20px 60px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                      Complete Your Profile Now ‚Üí
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Profile Lifecycle Info -->
              <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 25px; margin-top: 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 15px; font-weight: 700;">üí° What Happens Next?</p>
                <ul style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                  <li>Profile starts in <strong style="color: #F59E0B;">Pending</strong> status</li>
                  <li>After submission: <strong style="color: #3B82F6;">Under Review</strong></li>
                  <li>Once approved: <strong style="color: #10B981;">Published</strong> & live</li>
                  <li>Future updates require re-approval</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- Security Reminder -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15) 0%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; padding: 25px; margin-top: 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #FCA5A5; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  <strong style="color: #F87171;">üîê Security Reminder:</strong> Never share your password. Our team will never ask for it via email or phone. If you didn't expect this email, please contact support immediately.
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 40px 0 0;">
                Best of luck with your campaign!<br>
                <strong style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8B5CF6, #06B6D4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; font-size: 18px;">The ITFY E-Voting Team</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);">
              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px;">
                <a href="mailto:support@itfy-evoting.com" style="color: #8B5CF6; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Contact Support</a> | 
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="color: #06B6D4; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Candidate Portal</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; margin: 10px 0 0;">
                ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>